N.Y. Comp. Codes R. & Regs. Tit. 9 ยง 4202.6 - American Quarter Horse Association

State Regulations

The commission shall inform the American Quarter Horse

Association of its rules and regulations and any changes therein and all
penalties imposed which shall be of interest to it. Notes
